lead_paragraph: Sri Lanka took three wickets in the last three overs to snatch a thrilling one-run victory over West Indies in the triangular  one-day series on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Sri Lanka Snatch Thrilling Victory Over Wasteful Windies
